external_knowledge:
-modules under construction refers to modules with a status of 'in progress'; 
-modules can only be under one of the following statuses: planned, in progress, or completed;
-materials can be sourced from either a Manufacturing facility or the Market;
-the carbon footprint of a material is a measure of its environmental impact.

sql:
SELECT modules.module_name, materials.product
FROM modules
JOIN materials ON modules.module_id = materials.module_id;

SELECT SUM(value) AS total_value
FROM materials
WHERE supplier_id = 1 AND category_id = 1;

SELECT material_id, product, value, source_type, recyclable
FROM materials
WHERE source_type = 'Manufacturing facility' AND value > 700 AND recyclable = 1;
